Package: SIDFEx
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the Sea Ice Drift Forecast Experiment (SIDFEx)
Version: 0.3.1
Author: Helge Goessling and Simon Reifenberg
Maintainer: Helge Goessling <helge.goessling@awi.de>
Description: The package includes tools for: Data handling (download / write forecasts and observations); Data searching, viewing, selection, and plotting; Data analysis (error evolution, ensemble spread, ...); Data formatting; Generating simple benchmark forecasts (drift persistence, ...). For more information on SIDFEx, see http://www.polarprediction.net/yopp-activities/sidfex/ .
